nhc_headline: ...NARDA HAS BECOME A REMNANT LOW... ...THIS IS THE LAST ADVISORY...
summary: ...NARDA HAS BECOME A REMNANT LOW... ...THIS IS THE LAST ADVISORY... As of 8:00 PM PDT Sun Sep 28 the center of Narda was located near 20.9, -125.1 with movement NNE at 6 mph. The minimum central pressure was 1009 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 35 mph.
